&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;Tenstorrent is leading the industry on cutting-edge AI technology, revolutionizing performance expectations, ease of use, and cost efficiency. With AI redefining the computing paradigm, solutions must evolve to unify innovations in software models, compilers, platforms, networking, and semiconductors. Our diverse team of technologists have developed a high performance RISC-V CPU from scratch, and share a passion for AI and a deep desire to build the best AI platform possible. We value collaboration, curiosity, and a commitment to solving hard problems. We are growing our team and looking for contributors of all seniorities.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div&gt;
&lt;p class=&quot;p1&quot;&gt;Tenstorrent is leading the industry on cutting-edge AI technology, revolutionizing performance expectations, ease of use, and cost efficiency. With AI redefining the computing paradigm, solutions must evolve to unify innovations in software models, compilers, platforms, networking, and semiconductors. Our diverse team of technologists have developed a high performance RISC-V CPU from scratch, and share a passion for AI and a deep desire to build the best AI platform possible. We value collaboration, curiosity, and a commitment to solving hard problems. We are growing our team and looking for contributors of all seniorities.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;This role is on-site based in Santa Clara, CA.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who You Are:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;603&quot; data-end=&quot;660&quot;&gt;Background in computer science, ML, or a related field.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Comfortable in C/C++ and Python, with one or more FPGA or embedded projects under your belt (coursework counts).&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Exposed to digital design; Verilog, SystemVerilog, or VHDL and comfortable reasoning about clocks, FIFOs, and streaming interfaces.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;At home in Linux and on the command line; version control with git is second nature.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Curious about how hardware, firmware, and software fit together — and not intimidated by unfamiliar layers of the stack.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What We Need:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Someone to prototype and bring up hardware-software integrations between FPGA platforms and Tenstorrent accelerator cards.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write and extend host-side tooling and firmware that drives high-speed links between devices.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build test harnesses, measure end-to-end latency and throughput, and help turn prototypes into validated features.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You Will Learn:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How modern accelerators actually talk to each other.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;FPGA design and debug flows on production-grade hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Firmware development for embedded cores in a large SoC.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;How to ship software that runs on real customer hardware.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;Tenstorrent offers a highly competitive compensation package and benefits, and we are an equal opportunity employer.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;content-conclusion&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This offer of employment is contingent upon the applicant being eligible to access U.S. export-controlled technology. Due to U.S. export laws, including those codified in the U.S. Export Administration Regulations (EAR), the Company is required to ensure compliance with these laws when transferring technology to nationals of certain countries (such as EAR Country Groups D:1, E1, and E2). These requirements apply to persons located in the U.S. and all countries outside the U.S. As the position offered will have direct and/or indirect access to information, systems, or technologies subject to these laws, the offer may be contingent upon your citizenship/permanent residency status or ability to obtain prior license approval from the U.S. Commerce Department or applicable federal agency. If employment is not possible due to U.S. export laws, any offer of employment will be rescinded.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
